# Runtime data — these are produced by consumer repos using budai,
# never by budai itself. Listed here so that if anyone ever runs
# the OS against itself for dogfooding, the runtime artifacts stay out.
.agents/runs/
.agents/council/
.agents/messages/
.agents/stats/
.agents/index/

# Local-only when registry-source: self (workaround until task-011 librarian sync implements
# auto-populating .agents/base/ from repo-root base/). See findings.md F020.
.agents/base

